戒三日口 清得好乾淨 仲有相睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700b7dc2e391d19bdc2fbb4224dbdd27c1074f15","tid":404801,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"年頭照完腸 洗得好乾淨 內鏡可以拍片 見醫生仲幫我沖d腸壁屎漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63eb06cc788c9be6dc94250db96ef738e947836","tid":404801,"uid":122980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年頭照完腸 洗得好乾淨 內鏡可以拍片 見醫生仲幫我沖d腸壁屎漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c75a6643a782c7aac12a20bf8f3311041588ab","tid":404801,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年頭照完腸 洗得好乾淨 內鏡可以拍片 見醫生仲幫我沖d腸壁屎漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ada42002f6d6ce11af3ad3ed7a93e27af417fe","tid":404801,"uid":68038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:54:19.000Z","msg":"我自己便秘就會飲咖啡 <br />\n多數幾個鐘內就會想痾<br />\n同埋行多d路，做下運動都會好快有得痾"},{"pid":"057fdbc98c8a6758bffc9deac97d11693965de2f","tid":404801,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/130711_620057790fa71a7332991e6f817d3006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F130711_620057790fa71a7332991e6f817d3006.jpg&h=268a9b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTry this<br />\n<br />\n再屙唔到你應該睇醫生而唔係去洗腸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食多d菜就得<br />\n呢個好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a56db2f4195bf5510fb2e97835a1e35988f4ec","tid":404801,"uid":73697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"點解冇人提火龍果既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/4145104/art/20140707/18790350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F4145104%2Fart%2F20140707%2F18790350&d=4ZXabHcFZBev3dktCAp0NARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=00b1534f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F4145104%2Fart%2F20140707%2F18790350&h=35b36e17\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/4145104/art/20140707/18790350</a>"}]}